  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients undergoing atrial flutter ablation will be randomized to either the standard
      ablation approach or voltage targeted approach. Patients will be followed for one year to
      assess outcome of the ablation technique
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
